            <title>[SYNAPSE-240] Issue posting to JMS 1.0.x Topics</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-240</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using JMS 1.0.x, a &quot;Destination&quot; returned by a JNDI lookup with some providers (SwiftMQ 2.1.2) can implement both the Queue and Topic interfaces..  This causes the JMS sender to assume its posting to a Queue&lt;/p&gt;</description>
